</p>
<p>In the app directory, create a new class called <code>LittleKernel</code>. The kernel is the
heart of your application: make it extend the base <code>Kernel</code> class:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="13d96e4db4">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-8" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
