</p>
<p>Normally, this class <em>must</em> implement two abstract methods: <code>registerBundles()</code> and
<code>registerContainerConfiguration()</code>. But let's <em>not</em> implement those. Instead, use
the new <code>MicroKernelTrait</code>:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="7ad8bce4ae">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
