<p>We only need <em>one</em> bundle: <code>FrameworkBundle</code>. To configure that bundle, head to
<code>configureContainer()</code>, call <code>$c-&gt;loadFromExtension()</code>, and pass it <code>framework</code> and
an array of configuration. The only key it <em>needs</em> is <code>secret</code>. Set it to the top
secret super cool-kids password: <code>micr0</code>:</p>
