<h3 id="loading-external-routing-files">Loading External Routing Files <a class="headerlink" href="micro-kernel#loading-external-routing-files" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h3>
<p>Next, we need to load the annotation routes. That's <em>super</em> easy.</p>
<p>Use <code>$routes-&gt;import()</code>. Pass it whatever routing resource you want, like a YAML
or XML file. In our case, import the annotations from the <code>Controller</code> directory with
<code>__DIR__.'/../src/AppBundle/Controller'</code>. Pass <code>/</code> as the second argument - that's
the prefix - and <code>annotation</code> - the "type" - as the last arg:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="c84bea9fd6">
